en-US.dark: Applies the dark theme variant to the component. You can find more information on the Material Design documentation for [dark themes](https://material.io/design/color/dark-theme.html).
en-US.height: Sets the height for the component.
en-US.light: Applies the light theme variant to the component.
en-US.maxHeight: Sets the maximum height for the component.
en-US.maxWidth: Sets the maximum width for the component.
en-US.minHeight: Sets the minimum height for the component.
en-US.minWidth: Sets the minimum width for the component.
en-US.width: Sets the width for the component.
